  "contentHtml": "\n                                    \n                                                                                    <ul>\n                                                                                                                                                    <li><a href=\"/agency/87654375/PTI\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">PTI</a></li>\n                                                                                            </ul>\n                                                                                <ul>\n                                                                                            <li>Published On Jul 5, 2026 at 12:20 PM IST</li>\n                                                                                                                                </ul>\n                                    \n                                \n\n                    <!-- Display video article in news article for the custom next story -->\n                    \n                    <!-- Modifying the body placing embeds,promoslots,related etc.-->\n                                        <figure><img src=\"/images/default.jpg\" alt=\"\"></figure><p>Bengaluru: OnCare announced the launch of its new cancer treatment centre. The company said the facility marked a significant step in its mission to make <a href=\"/tag/high-quality+cancer+care\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">high-quality cancer care</a> more accessible, affordable and patient-friendly across India.The expansion follows OnCare's successful operations in the Delhi-NCR region, where it says it has built a reputation for delivering comprehensive oncology services through a model focused on convenience, affordability, clinical excellence and patient experience, according to a statement.</p><!-- PROMOSLOT_M --><p>\"Our goal has always been to ensure that no cancer patient has to struggle unnecessarily to access quality treatment,\" said Deepak Kumar, Founder of OnCare.</p>\n                            <p>Advt\n                            </p>\n\n                              \n                                                         \n                        <p>\"Cancer treatment is already physically and emotionally demanding. The healthcare system should not make it harder. We built OnCare to offer expert-led, compassionate and accessible care that puts patients and families first,\" he added.</p><!-- PROMOSLOT_M --><p>According to the company, the newly launched centre aims to address the growing need for specialised cancer care in the city and surrounding regions.The centre will offer chemotherapy, immunotherapy, targeted therapy, oncology consultations, treatment planning, supportive care services and patient navigation programmes, it added.                    </p><!-- Category Most Read Placement -->\n                                                                    \n                                                                \n                                <ul>\n                                    \n\n                                                                        <li><a href=\"/agency/87654375/PTI\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">PTI</a></li>\n                                </ul>\n                                <ul>\n                                    <!-- <li> Updated On Jul 5, 2026 at 12:20 PM IST</li> -->\n                                    <li>Published On Jul 5, 2026 at 12:20 PM IST</li>\n                                    <!-- <li class=\"desktop-view\">1 min read</li> -->\n                                </ul>\n                            \n                                        \n\n                    \n\n                    <!-- Comment Section -->\n                                            \n                                        <!-- Comment Section -->\n\n                    \n                      \n    \n            <p>\n     